{"id":49,"type":"vertex","label":"sourcegraph:documentationString","result":{"kind":"markdown","value":"```Go\ntype TodoItem struct {\n\tTodo string `json:\"todo\"`\n\tDue  string `json:\"due,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\nTodoItem is the internal type used to store the JSON data that is deserialised by the app. \n\n"}}
